ZH: 他们在喜庆活动中燃放了烟花。
EN: They set off fireworks during the celebration.

ZH: 每年春节，人们都会燃放鞭炮以驱除邪灵。
EN: Every Chinese New Year, people set off firecrackers to drive away evil spirits.

ZH: 燃放烟火应该在指定的地点进行。
EN: Fireworks should be set off in designated areas.

ZH: 孩子们高兴地燃放了彩色的焰火。
EN: The children joyfully set off colorful fireworks.

ZH: 请不要在居民区燃放烟花。
EN: Please do not set off fireworks in residential areas.

ZH: 在万圣节，人们会燃放灯火来庆祝。
EN: People set off lanterns to celebrate Halloween.

ZH: 燃放烟花时一定要小心安全。
EN: Be careful with safety when setting off fireworks.

ZH: 他们在庆祝活动中燃放了烟火。
EN: They set off fireworks during the celebration event.

ZH: 球迷们燃放了红色和蓝色的焰火。
EN: Fans set off red and blue fireworks.

ZH: 燃放这么多烟花会对环境产生负面影响。
EN: Setting off so many fireworks will have a negative impact on the environment.

ZH: 小心燃放烟雾弹，以免造成伤害。
EN: Be careful when setting off smoke bombs to avoid injury.

ZH: 在节日里，人们惯常燃放烟火庆祝。
EN: People traditionally set off fireworks to celebrate during holidays.

ZH: 警方在燃放烟花活动中保持秩序。
EN: The police maintain order during firework displays.

ZH: 他们计划在公园里燃放烟火。
EN: They plan to set off fireworks in the park.

ZH: 面对干旱季节，燃放烟火可能会引发火灾。
EN: During dry seasons, setting off fireworks can cause wildfires.

